<section id="testimonials" class="testimonials-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Trusted by Developers & Agencies</h2>
      <p>See what builders say about our automation robots</p>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonials-grid">
      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"This is legitimately game-changing. The SEO Robot found content gaps I completely missed and generated perfectly optimized articles in minutes."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="avatar">👨‍💻</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>Marcus Rodriguez</strong>
            <span>SaaS Founder</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"Newsletter Robot saved us 10+ hours weekly. The Exa AI integration finds incredibly relevant content our audience actually wants to read."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="avatar">👩‍💼</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>Sarah Chen</strong>
            <span>Content Director</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"The Article Robot's competitor analysis is insane. It scraped 20 competitor sites, found gaps, and generated unique content in under 15 minutes."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="avatar">🧑‍🚀</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>David Kumar</strong>
            <span>Marketing Agency Owner</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"Finally, AI automation that actually works as promised. The Pydantic validation ensures quality, and the outputs are consistently excellent."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="avatar">👨‍🔬</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>Alex Thompson</strong>
            <span>Tech Lead</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"We replaced 3 different tools with this suite. SEO, newsletters, and articles all automated. ROI paid for itself in the first month."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="avatar">👩‍🎨</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>Emily Park</strong>
            <span>Growth Marketer</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="testimonial-card">
        <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
        <p class="quote">"The topical flow analysis and internal linking recommendations are exactly what we needed. Our organic traffic is up 47% in 8 weeks."</p>
        <div class="author">
          <div class="avatar">🧑‍💼</div>
          <div class="author-info">
            <strong>James Wilson</strong>
            <span>E-commerce Owner</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonials-section {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    background: white;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--color-light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .testimonial-card:hover {
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
  }

  .stars {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .quote {
    color: var(--color-dark);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .avatar {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    width: 50px;
    height: 50px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .author-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .author-info strong {
    color: var(--color-dark);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .author-info span {
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-header h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .testimonials-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
